OL,3,CMan, 36, spotted with 'handgun' in
OL,4,CWest Yorkshire
OL,6,FWest Yorkshire Police received reports
OL,7,Flast night of a man walking around
OL,8,FBradford with what appeared to be a
OL,9,Fhandgun.
OL,11,FArmed officers headed to Frank Street,
OL,12,Fnear Horton Park, and fired a soft-
OL,13,Fnosed projectile and a man was
OL,14,Fdetained.
OL,16,FThe man, 36, has since been arrested
OL,17,Fon suspicion of possession of an
OL,18,Fimitation firearm with intent to cause
OL,19,Ffear of violence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
